<a href="post_856715.html#856715"><img src="templates/fisubgreen/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" class="imgspace" width="12" height="9" alt="Сообщение" title="Сообщение" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails"><font color=black>Добавлено: Пт 21 Май 2010, 12:06</font><IDXSKIP><span class="gen"><br></IDXSKIP>
